\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 Open}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  command identifies which outline you wish to work on. The }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 Save}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  command will save the file with the same name it with which it was opened or previously saved. The }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 Save As}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  command will save an outline under a new name or at a new location. }
