\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx-720\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 This dialog will by default display recently opened outlines. Clicking on }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 Open story from disk}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  will open a file browser to allow you to pick a particular outline to pen.  Clicking on the}{\f1\fs24\b1\i0  Create new story }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 tab on the left will display a dialog for a new story outline. The}{\f1\fs24\b1\i0  Project path}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  defaults to the file folder specified in }{\f1\fs24\b1\i0 Preferences}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 .}
